## 👨‍💻 Developer Notes

- Frontend uses Bootstrap 5 for base components
- Custom CSS overrides Bootstrap for modern fancy UI
- All passwords are hashed before storage
- Sessions expire based on Redis TTL configuration
- Profile data is stored separately in MongoDB for scalability

